The paper proposes a new learning framework for reinforcement learning that uses an ensemble of policies to act in the environment while periodically sharing knowledge amongst policies in the ensemble through knowledge distillation. This involves techniques from machine learning, artificial intelligence, robotics, and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
